change with 30 days' notice."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Units are rented on a first-come, first-served basis. Availability is indicated on our website but is subject to change."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl text-white mt-8","children":"5. Payment Terms"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Payments are processed securely online. All prices are in South African Rand (ZAR). Payment must be made in advance for the selected rental term. Late payments may result in loss of access to your unit."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We accept Visa and Mastercard credit cards. Debit cards are not accepted for online payments at this time."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl text-white mt-8","children":"6. Access and Hours"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Access to the storage facility is available during the following hours:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Monday to Friday: 08:00 – 17:00"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Saturday: 09:00 – 13:00"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Sunday and Public Holidays: Closed"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Hours may change seasonally. We will provide notice of any changes."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl text-white mt-8","children":"7. Prohibited Items"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"You may not store the following items in your unit:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Perishable goods, food, or living plants"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Flammable or explosive materials"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Hazardous chemicals or substances"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Illegal goods or materials"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Radioactive materials"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Asbestos or toxic waste"}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl text-white mt-8","children":"8. Security and Liability"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"While our facility is equipped with 24/7 CCTV surveillance and perimeter security, National Secure Storage is not responsible for loss or damage to stored items due to theft, fire, flood, or other events beyond our control. We strongly recommend that you obtain insurance for valuable items."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"You are responsible for providing your own padlock for your unit."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl text-white mt-8","children":"9. Cancellation and Termination"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"You may cancel your rental at any time by providing 30 days' written notice (email acceptable). Refunds are calculated on a pro-rata basis for unused days of the rental period. A R150 cancellation admin fee applies to monthly contracts."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl text-white mt-8","children":"10. Right of Entry"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We reserve the right to enter your storage unit in the following circumstances:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Emergency situations (fire, flood, gas leak)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Maintenance or repairs"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Compliance with legal requirements"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Suspected illegal activity (with law enforcement)"}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl text-white mt-8","children":"11. Intellectual Property"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and software, is the property of National Secure Storage and is protected by copyright laws."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl text-white mt-8","children":"12. Limitation of Liability"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"To the maximum extent permitted by law, National Secure Storage shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of our services."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl text-white mt-8","children":"13. Changes to Terms"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Use at any time. C